commitMessage:
Fix user menu null reference errors and improve auth state handling

- Add null checks in UserMenu component to prevent errors when user data is null
- Improve auth state initialization to ensure both token and user data are valid
- Add fallback values for user name and email in UserMenu
- Clear auth state when user data is invalid
